      <title>戴利称美联储可以慢慢应对特朗普的政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/daly-says-fed-can-take-its-time-in-reacting-to-trump-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山联邦储备银行行长玛丽·戴利表示，美国经济状况良好，央行不需要对特朗普政府推出的政策做出迅速反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/daly-says-fed-can-take-its-time-in-reacting-to-trump-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 19:44:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院委员会支持加巴德的任命，她将获得确认</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gabbard-on-path-to-confirmation-after-senate-committee-backs-her</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前众议员塔尔西·加巴德 (Tulsi Gabbard) 获得参议院情报委员会的认可，担任唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的间谍部门负责人，为参议院的确认投票铺平了道路，尽管她过去的立场受到批评，包括支持泄露绝密计划的美国情报承包商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gabbard-on-path-to-confirmation-after-senate-committee-backs-her</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 19:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会被敦促保护联邦统计数据免受特朗普“清洗”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/congress-urged-to-protect-federal-statistics-from-trump-purge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个联邦统计倡导组织正在敦促国会恢复特朗普政府删除的所有政府数据并防止此类事件再次发生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/congress-urged-to-protect-federal-statistics-from-trump-purge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 19:25:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大科技领袖成立团体影响政治动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/canada-tech-leaders-launch-group-to-influence-political-upheaval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在加拿大顶尖科技企业家的支持下，一个团体发起了一项活动，旨在在今年大选前推行政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/canada-tech-leaders-launch-group-to-influence-political-upheaval</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 19:10:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FBI 特工起诉司法部，要求其停止披露 1 月 6 日的调查角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/fbi-agents-sue-doj-to-stop-disclosure-of-roles-in-jan-6-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两组联邦调查局特工正在寻求法院命令，阻止唐纳德·特朗普总统的司法部保存和公布调查 1 月 6 日国会大厦袭击事件的局内员工名单，他们表示担心这份名单可能被用来对他们进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/fbi-agents-sue-doj-to-stop-disclosure-of-roles-in-jan-6-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 19:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫称首批移民航班正在飞往关塔那摩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/white-house-says-first-migrant-flights-to-guantanamo-underway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府首批搭载被拘留移民前往关塔那摩湾的航班将于周二起飞，此前总统下令大规模准备将数千名囚犯送往古巴的美国海军基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/white-house-says-first-migrant-flights-to-guantanamo-underway</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 18:34:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财政部从马斯克的 DOGE 团队中吸纳两名成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/us-treasury-brings-in-two-members-from-musk-s-doge-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国财政部已引进至少两名与所谓的政府效率部有关的人员：云软件集团公司 (Cloud Software Group Inc.) 首席执行官汤姆·克劳斯 (Tom Krause) 和曾在 SpaceX 和社交媒体平台 X 工作的工程师马尔科·埃莱兹 (Marko Elez)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/us-treasury-brings-in-two-members-from-musk-s-doge-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 17:16:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普指示官员加大对伊朗的经济压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-direct-officials-to-ramp-up-economic-pressure-on-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统签署了一项指令，旨在加大对伊朗的经济压力，履行其前任总统所承诺的扭转宽松制裁执行制度的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-direct-officials-to-ramp-up-economic-pressure-on-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:41:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“这太离奇了”：特朗普冻结气候资金引发恐惧和困惑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/-it-s-surreal-trump-s-freeze-on-climate-money-sows-fear-and-confusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 1 月 27 日特朗普政府下令停止发放联邦补助金后，一些环保非营利组织和研究人员仍然无法获得补助金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/-it-s-surreal-trump-s-freeze-on-climate-money-sows-fear-and-confusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克和阿克曼离职后，特拉华州著名的商业法庭受到州长的严厉审视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/as-musk-and-ackman-snub-delaware-governor-looks-hard-at-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个多世纪以来，特拉华州一直拥有美国首屈一指的商业法庭，是大多数财富 500 强公司和美国最大公司诉讼的合法审理地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/as-musk-and-ackman-snub-delaware-governor-looks-hard-at-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 14:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
